The,CTA,Bus,Tracker,API,provides,a,gateway,into,near,real,time,CTA,bus,locations,and,estimated,arrival,times,Developers,can,use,the,official,CTA,Bus,Tracker,service,via,Web,or,mobile,device,The,API,allows,developers,to,get,specific,information,from,Bus,Tracker,to,incorporate,estimated,arrivals,and,location,information,into,apps,Data,exposed,via,the,API,includes,vehicle,locations,route,data,prediction,data,and,service,bulletins,The,API,uses,RESTful,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,XML